<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV75">
<l>oṉṟiniṉṟu naltavañcey tūḻiyūḻi tōṟelām</l>
<l>niṉṟuniṉṟa vaṉkuṇaṅka ḷuḷḷiyuḷḷan tūyarāy</l>
<l>ceṉṟuceṉṟu tēvatēva rumparumpa rumparāy</l>
<l>aṉṟiyeṅkaḷ ceṅkaṇmālai yāvarkāṇa vallarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Performing good penance with a focused [mind] in each and all aeons,</l>
<l>Becoming purified at heart thinking of His qualities progressively,</l>
<l>Going further and further and becoming higher, higher, and higher,</l>
<l>Which other god of gods can see our red-eyed Māl?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
